{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "239d919b-9d63-4ee0-9b5d-477787c9d528",
    "name": "WP-ERP App Helper — Notes & Labels API",
    "description": "Namespace: erp-app/v1\n\n**Auth flow:**\n1. Call **Login** — saves `token` automatically.\n2. All subsequent requests use `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` (set at collection level).\n3. Optionally call **Register Biometric** to get a `biometric_token` for fingerprint login.\n\n**Collection variables to set before first run:**\n- `base_url` — site URL, no trailing slash (e.g. `http://wp-erp.test`)\n- `wp_username` — WordPress username\n- `wp_password` — WordPress password\n\nAll other variables (`token`, `biometric_token`, `label_id`, `note_id`, `attachment_id`) are captured automatically by test scripts.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "16239892"
  },
